Summary:        Extra Haskell functions

License:        BSD-3-Clause
URL:            https://hackage.haskell.org/package/extra
# Begin cabal-rpm sources:
Source0:        https://hackage.haskell.org/package/%{pkgver}/%{pkgver}.tar.gz
